    <abstract>
      <t>A Network Resource Partition (NRP) is a network resource attribute associated with the SR policy. It is also an important attribute of the SR policy and needs to be reported to the external components. This document defines a new TLV which enable the headend to report the configuration and the states of an SR policy carrying the NRP information by using BPG-LS.</t>
